    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Living Shadows</strong>是一款恐怖生存游戏，玩家需要扮演一位名叫艾米莉亚的女性，穿越亡灵世界，拯救自己的妹妹，并设法回到现实世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >又是一天的工作之后，阿米莉亚发现自己被拉进了一个属于死人的世界。在那里，她发现自己的妹妹被绑架了，于是她开始拯救妹妹，走出这场噩梦。一路上，她遇到了一个神秘的女人，她试图帮助她，指引她走上正确的道路。这个世界充满危险，到处都是怪物，只有少数人愿意帮助阿米莉亚生存下去。您必须找出阿米莉亚能否救出她的妹妹并走出亡灵世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-恐怖生存游戏[/h2］ <br>在这个残酷的世界里，你必须利用一切可用资源来生存，怪物会让你流血、减速甚至感染。探索地点、撬开门锁、寻找补给，以求生存。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c758dc5c2823bce09107a624f6ba9356.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c758dc5c2823bce09107a624f6ba9356.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c758dc5c2823bce09107a624f6ba9356.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>- 库存管理容量有限的传统库存将迫使您决定带什么、留什么。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c1bab06a8a9bfd1a7a54dcdbe8458558.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c1bab06a8a9bfd1a7a54dcdbe8458558.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/c1bab06a8a9bfd1a7a54dcdbe8458558.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。 <br> <br>- 技能您可以让艾米莉亚和她的武器变得更强，解锁新的能力，这些能力将在未来对您有所帮助。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/b990bc9c60f0a5fe157d308a036fc165.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/b990bc9c60f0a5fe157d308a036fc165.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/b990bc9c60f0a5fe157d308a036fc165.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。 <br> <br>- 种类繁多的怪物在这款游戏中，您会发现各种各样的敌人，从普通的僵尸到巨大的怪兽。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/dd392cd224899719e9926e849a20f733.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/dd392cd224899719e9926e849a20f733.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/dd392cd224899719e9926e849a20f733.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. <br> <br>- 不同的地点和游戏持续时间[/h2］ <br>许多不同的地点在等着你，每个地点都与前一个地点大不相同。此外，如果您决定探索周围的世界，那么游戏时间将相当漫长。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/d4d8b50dc1f93cbab512992f62afb198.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/d4d8b50dc1f93cbab512992f62afb198.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/d4d8b50dc1f93cbab512992f62afb198.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。 <br> <br>[与角色对话[/h2］ <br>游戏中会有几个角色，他们都会影响艾米莉亚的故事。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/5dfd962acfa16d053263fffdf277d79e.poster.avif?t=1761920476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/5dfd962acfa16d053263fffdf277d79e.webm?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138480/extras/5dfd962acfa16d053263fffdf277d79e.mp4?t=1761920476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 多种结局</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏将有两个结局和一个决定性的选择。拯救妹妹将决定阿米莉亚的故事结局。</h2>",
